Apa? Saya tidak...

01:13:26.919 --> 01:13:28.714
Apa yang awak
cakapkan ni?

01:13:31.061 --> 01:13:33.650
Anak patung itu...

01:13:33.685 --> 01:13:35.169
awak.

01:13:39.587 --> 01:13:41.002
Fiona?

01:13:43.177 --> 01:13:44.489
Sial!

01:13:45.593 --> 01:13:47.250
Fiona tahu?

